    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>free range chicken breast portion[s]</strong> to the plate with the <strong>Cajun-style seasoning</strong> and press into the spices to coat evenly – this is your <strong>coated</strong> <strong>chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1715605152534-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1715605152534-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1715605152534-x700.jpg",
